detailed instructions at:
https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMS/MadgraphInterface

Some LHE files for testing can be found in:
/castor/cern.ch/user/d/dkcira/MadGraph/Samples
small_example_ttbar.lhe		<- example file with events in the Les Houches format for MadGraph, full sample is in /castor/cern.ch/user/d/dkcira/MadGraph/Samples/example_ttbar.lhe
small_example_phantom_mc.lhe	<- example file with events in the Les Houches format for the Phantom MC


The last version of the old style cfg files is kept in the subdirectory OldStyleCfgs/
